'''Abuferriw''' neɣ '''Tawacult n ibuferriwen''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: '''Paridae''') d [[tawacult (tasnudert)|tawacult]] n [[agṭiṭ|yigṭaṭ]] yettidiren deg [[Amadal amzikan|umadal amzikan]] d [[Tamrikt n Ugafa|Marikan n Ugafa]], Abuferriw d afrux meẓẓiyen, [[ableɣ|ableɣ-is]] yettili gar n 10 cm ar 22 cm, Aṭas seg [[talmest|telmas]] n twacult-a ttidiren zdat n [[afgan|yimdanen]] anda ttafen učči-nsen am [[ifes|yifsan]].

