== Aglam ==
Anagar tiwsitin tiynelmasin, yakk [[talmest|tilmas]] n ubuferriw d tid yettemcabin s waṭas deg talɣa. Dɣa tawacult-a tettwassnen s wemcabi n yigmamen-is (tilmas-is) akk. Teɣzi tagejdant n telmas n ubuferriw yettili gar n 10 alamma 16 cm, yakk d 9 alamma d 21 cm i [[tawsit (tudersent)|tewsitin]] tiynelmasin, ma d [[azuk]] yettili gar n 7 ar 29 g yakk d 5 ar 49 g i tewsitin tiynelmasin, S umata ifurken igejdanen n ubuferriw ttaken-d seg yiniten yemgaraden n [[Afraw|wafrawen-is]]. 

'''[[Aqamum]]''' <br/>
Aqamum n ubuferriw meẓẓiy maca llan wid ihrawen d wid sdiden (rqiqen) s unect (ɛla ḥsab) n wučči ɣef wacu yegguni, Acku tilmas iy tetten [[aburɣas|iburɣas]] lant (sɛant) iqamumen sdiden, ma d tilmas iy tetten ifsan iqamumen-nsent zhur-it.

== Ideggan n tudert ==
Abuferriw d [[Ijqiwen|ajqiw]] yettidiren deg waṭas n yidgan n umadal anda yettidir deg umur ameqran n [[amenẓaw|imenẓawen]] n [[Turuft|Uruppa]] d [[Asya]] d [[Tafriqt|Tefriqt]] d [[Tamrikt n Ugafa|Marikan n Ugafa]], Ula di [[Tamurt n Leqbayel|tmurt n Iqbayliyen]] llant kra n telmas am [[Tamzilt|ubuferriw azegzaw]].

